Lucy Davis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucy_Davis 0 Lucy Clare Davis (born 17 February 1973) is an English actress. She played the role of Dawn Tinsley in the BBC comedy The Office, as well as Dianne in the horror-comedy movie Shaun of the Dead, Hayley in The Archers, and Etta Candy in Wonder Woman. Davis stars as Hilda Spellman in the Netflix series Chilling Adventures of Sabrina. Lucy_Clare_Davis ( born 17_February_1973 ) is an_English_actress .
